SELECT account_no,customer,lp_description,lp_from_range,lp_to_range,lp_src_realm,lp_nextrealm_list,lp_nexthop_list,lp_active,"chargeTypes"
FROM public.gen1_ntwk_data 
WHERE (lp_src_realm ILIKE '%optus%' AND (lp_src_realm ILIKE '%byoc%' OR lp_src_realm  ILIKE '%iselect%' OR lp_src_realm ILIKE '%bunnings%' OR lp_src_realm ILIKE '%iag%')) OR (lp_src_realm ILIKE '%byoc%' OR dest_byoc = 'true' OR "chargeTypes" ILIKE '%byoc%') AND lp_src_realm IS NOT NULL
